      <title>瑞银前老板退出家族办公室 财富 80 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/ex-ubs-boss-exits-family-office-for-8-billion-walgreens-fortune</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团(UBS Group AG)前高管辞去了亿万富翁斯特凡诺·佩西纳(Stefano Pessina)家族办公室负责人的职务，结束了长达数十年的业务关系，而这种关系曾帮助沃尔格林博茨联盟公司(Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.)董事长积累了财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/ex-ubs-boss-exits-family-office-for-8-billion-walgreens-fortune</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
